<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="thunder-vi">thunder <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'θʌndə(r)/    美 /'θʌndər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>打雷；发出雷鸣般的声响：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>It thundered a few times, but no rain fell. 
打了几声雷，但没下雨。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The train thundered through the small station. 
火车轰隆隆地驶过那个小站。</p></div></div>